<br>
If you look at the Calendar you will see that nobody else is making such a territory grab. You have 12 hours to do Hate. That is because respawns there are 12 hours, not 24-72. <br>
<br>
Raids in hate with a reservation are allowed to be there for the length of the raid dependant on the respawn time of the mobs there. Since Hate is 12 hours, you have 12 hours. Therefore the Raging Boar raid scheduled for 13 hours after your raid begins is well within the calendar rules.<br>
<br>
However, the Raging Boars has merged with 4 other guilds and has a new name, Infinitus Vindicat. As such we are only keeping one reservation on the calendar and have decided to take our July 1st date that had been one of our member guilds slots. I will be therefore removing the RB slot on July 14th, however if this slot remains open after our July 1st raid,I will be re-issuing a reservation for 13 hours after yours starts. <br>
<br>
So I suggest either you change your time slot or be prepared for someone else to take our place. You have 12 hours for Hate, as does everyone else on the server.<br>
<br>
Barsh em gud! <br>
<br>
